            <span class="p-2">@(role)</span><span class="p-2">@(userName)</span>已登入
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-cols-2 row-cols-lg-4">
        <div class="p-5">
            <div class="custom-link-box m-auto d-flex flex-column position-relative">
